        {
            "title": "道指曾升336點收跌152點　納指標指再齊創新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美股5月開局個別發展，納斯達克指數與標普500同創新高，道瓊斯工業平均指數倒跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/3e4d531c5ffa6b2ea91eb8a3c84b5822_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_911__FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/3e4d531c5ffa6b2ea91eb8a3c84b5822_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_911__FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">道瓊斯工業平均指數走勢反覆，高開180點，升幅擴大至最多336點，高見49988點，其後掉頭回落，最終收報49499點，跌152點或0.31%，以貼近全日低位收市。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">納斯達克指數收報25114點，升222點或0.89%；標準普爾500指數收報7230點，升21點或0.29%，兩者齊創收市新高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">總結全星期，三大指數均錄得升幅，道指累升0.55%，納指升1.12%，標普500指數升0.91%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">費城半導體指數收漲0.87%，報10595.341點，突破4月24日所創收盤歷史最高位，連漲五周。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場憧憬美伊舉行新一輪談判，加上企業業績強勁，利好投資氣氛，但後段因特朗普稱將從下周開始，把歐盟汽車關稅上調至25%，納指標指升幅收窄，道指倒跌收市。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">蘋果公司上季業績勝預期，股價收升3.28%，曾飆5.8% ; 微軟及亞馬遜分別漲1.6%及1.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">雅詩蘭黛(Estee Lauder)宣布額外裁減3000職位，並且上調盈利預測，一度飆12.7%，收市仍升3.4%；遊戲平台Roblox用戶增長放慢，股價暴瀉18.3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">AMD收漲1.7%，博通升逾0.9%，台積電美股收漲0.4%，4月倍升的英特爾收升逾5.4%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15951979-%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e6%9b%be%e5%8d%87336%e9%bb%9e%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c152%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%80%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e6%a8%99%e6%8c%87%e5%86%8d%e9%bd%8a%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/74bf078b7e40b6a0d38033c9fe29a87b_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street_60099_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-02 10:28:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英股偏軟收市　法德股市休市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">歐洲多個主要股市，泛歐指數兩連升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260304_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：德國證交所官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260304_FI_source-web_eu-stock-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：德國證交所官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">泛歐600指數收升0.04%，報611.55點，本周累漲0.15%，最近六周內第五周累漲。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">英國股市表現偏軟，富時100指數收報10363點，跌14點，跌幅為0.14%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">主要歐洲國家股市：德國、法國、意大利、西班牙股市周五休市。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15951949-%e8%8b%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%e3%80%80%e6%b3%95%e5%be%b7%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e4%bc%91%e5%b8%82",
